                    "name": "Excorion Behemoths",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Specialized necromantic rituals are required to make larger excorions, as their blood vessels demand exponentially greater strength to move their larger body masses. These excorion behemoths are usually created from giants, elephants, dinosaurs, or even titans in rare instances. ",
